lender.name: Lisa4Jesus
lender.occupation: I work for Jesus doing whatever He leads me to do!
lender.loan_because:
First, the money I loan isn't really "mine", this money has literally come from Jesus Himself. Everything I currently have is only because of Him so instead of putting my own name here, I want everyone who receives money from me to thank Jesus Christ because He is the only reason I had it to give in the first place.
Jesus tells us to help others and I spend my life doing His work. I also loan because I know how hard it is out there. I've been unable to work myself for over 3 years now due to permanent injuries and have no income yet. In fact, I've had zero income for a very long time now and it's only been by the miraculous blessings of Jesus Christ Himself that I'm not homeless myself right now! State Disability ran out so I'm now waiting on Social Security Disability. However, God was gracious enough to give me a sum of money that I believe will pull me through until I start receiving Social Security Disability.
God was my only help through all my financial troubles so I wanted to use part of what He gave me to help others too. If not for His merciful blessings, I would be homeless right now, so I'm living proof that we can ALWAYS count on Jesus to provide us with what we "need", just like He told us in the Bible!
lender.occupational_info: I provide free Christian services such as free Christian movies, documentaries, t.v. shows, Bible study software, weekly Bible studies, and MUCH more! I also provide the latest scientific evidences in all the areas of science (including archeology, geology, creation science, etc.) that show us that the Bible is 100% true and accurate!
